drop table "BC_SpaceAdjustNewBooth" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "BC_SpaceAdjustNewBooth" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "BC_SpaceAdjustNewBooth"
(
"NewID" NUMBER(32) not null,
BCID NUMBER(32),
"FloorID" NUMBER(32),
"BoothCode" VARCHAR(20),
"ReallyArea" DECIMAL(20, 4),
"ShareRatio" DECIMAL(6, 2),
"BoothLevel" NVARCHAR2(100),
"CategoryID" NVARCHAR2(100),
"BudgetaryPrice" DECIMAL(20, 2),
"BoothDesc" NVARCHAR2(2000),
"VectorInfo" BLOB,
"CreatTime" TIMESTAMP,
"DoorplateRemarks" NVARCHAR2(2000),
"IsEffect" INTEGER default 0,
"MDReallyArea" DECIMAL(20, 4),
"FireLength" DECIMAL(6, 2),
"FireWidth" DECIMAL(6, 2),
"FireArea" DECIMAL(6, 2),
constraint PK_BC_SPACEADJUSTNEWBOOTH primary key ("NewID")
);

comment on column "BC_SpaceAdjustNewBooth"."CreatTime" is
'创建时间和展位编码确定原展位';

comment on column "BC_SpaceAdjustNewBooth"."IsEffect" is
'是否更新至当前经营图
0:未更新
1：已更新';

comment on column "BC_SpaceAdjustNewBooth"."MDReallyArea" is
'扣减设施后的实测面积';
